Disk World creator help
set_sell_stolen

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_sell_stolen -  This method sets the shop as a place which will receive and seel stolen goods.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_sell_stolen(int i)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - the new value for the stolen property

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/general_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the shop as a place which will receive and
seel stolen goods.  It automaticly sets the no_steal property
to 1.
.EP

